{"type": "article", "id": 44730, "title": "怎么把整骨治疗说清楚？来看看这间诊所的形象设计｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-08-31T23:05:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 43715, "name": "Ermolaev Bureau"}, {"id": 30736, "name": "wishlist"}, {"id": 30564, "name": "OTOTO"}, {"id": 43716, "name": "Off Grid Box"}, {"id": 43717, "name": "Maria Fabrizio"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 98, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170831181534gPpbeq8VuwtCIy0n.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Osteo Poly Clinic by Ermolaev Bureau</h3><p>想要三言两语把整骨治疗解释清楚可能有点麻烦，俄罗斯设计工作室 <a href=\"http://ermolaevbureau.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ermolaev Bureau</a> 为骨科诊所 Osteo Poly Clinic 设计的<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/42096829/Osteo-Poly-Clinic\" rel=\"nofollow\">品牌形象</a>就给出了一个简洁又美观的解决方案。设计团队将医生治疗病人所使用的五指拆分为由诊所名和半圆弧组成的五个元素，借此传递出整骨治疗的意义：只有当它们准确排列、弧线刚好构成一个圆圈时，身体才处于健康的状态。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181605BCb2ejxKMq9yw6Ul.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181605vQ7A3ToRplSX15G9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181604oCMZfzXyhUAVGsLJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181605EPphW6JrdlVws8b1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>E.P. LIGHT by E.P. design</h3><p>当发明家与艺术家携手，会诞生怎样的设计？最近，来自深圳的 E.P. design 工作坊决定将美国画家杰克逊·波洛克（Jackson Pollock）笔下著名的滴色画放进爱迪生灯泡之中，而名字中的 E.P. 刚好指的是爱迪生与波洛克姓氏首字母的组合。每个灯泡都由制作团队手工打造，里面浇注的是号称对环境无害的硅胶，加入颜料冷却后就成了独一无二的气氛灯。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/117334764/ep-light-when-inventor-meet-artist\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 16 澳元起。赞助者可以在集资结束后选择一个喜欢的颜色，制作团队会尽可能将其呈现在灯泡之中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708311816233kMRoANE1JUupInX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.495588\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181623EzFVtZcCn9vxrpJT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181623Qi862j9S3A7H1XOv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181623qxUkJzgu7syPZO0p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181623VfqlSUIBo4KAuFtL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tipsy by wishlist</h3><p>还记得那个<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/30229.html\">为海绵设计小床</a>的双人设计组合 <a href=\"http://www.wishlist-design.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">wishlist</a> 吗？最近这两位以色列女设计师再度与 OTOTO 合作，带来了这位爱喝葡萄酒的女巫 Tipsy。她的巫师帽和一双长腿可以帮助你轻松地固定住家中的美酒收藏，避免它们不小心滚动。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.ototodesign.com/collections/all-products/products/tipsy-bottle-stacker\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>预订这个小道具，售价为 15 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181639FVbgecLEywHlsNBA.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675676\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181638thKbpV4rxmJv05y2.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708311816385UHXDPhxAwyno3Tf.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708311816388ruvpUNiaMbHVBOQ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mindnosis by Sara Lopez Ibanez</h3><p>情绪或是精神上感到不佳，但又很难对全科医生（GP）开口，或是不知道如何解释自己的状态该怎么办？伦敦中央圣马丁学院的毕业生 Sara Lopez Ibanez 以自己 17 岁那年患上心理疾病的体验为参考，制作了这套名为 Mindnosis 的自我诊断工具。它包含四种不同功能的道具，其中包括用六种颜色代表的症状类型贴纸、手帐、自我诊断用的卡片以及解释症状并提供医疗机构联系方式的小册子。Ibanez 希望借此帮助人们更好地了解自己、与医生沟通。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181659raeh2vzM7RSkOYyj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181659WXbKgmor7awCUuic.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181659FR6hBPjTnSpab9QX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Off Grid Box</h3><p>在偏远贫困或是受灾地区，持续的电力与洁净水供给并不是件容易的事。考虑到庞大复杂的机器给运输和使用带来了不小的障碍，意大利初创公司 <a href=\"https://www.offgridbox.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Off Grid Box</a> 开发了一个大小只有 3 平方米左右的同名箱子，它的顶部装有太阳能电视板，内部藏有一个水库及净水系统，就像是一个既能供电又能供水的小型服务站。目前，Off Grid Box 一半的用户是非洲国家的非盈利组织，未来公司计划将它们安装在更多地点并与当地政府进行合作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181718obiDFZCBzeuxsvYL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715159\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708311817181EmujqUHp6vzer3k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181719ZnDdwY8t5EbMkTjW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181718MfrpVviH5BoOtYCx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746944\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181719WiQlL87dDvPBMROJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Wordless News by Maria Fabrizio</h3><p>和不少人一样，美国插画师 <a href=\"https://mariafabrizio.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maria Fabrizio</a> 每天早晨都有读新闻的习惯，而不同之处在于她会在读完之后将头条转化成插图，并将它们上传至名为 <a href=\"http://wordlessnews.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wordless News</a> 的个人博客。摈弃了有时看起来耸人听闻的文字标题，这些插图同样有着引起人们好奇的力量。今年以来，包括特朗普解雇 FBI 局长科米、通俄邮件，以及最近的夏洛茨维尔骚乱和日全食都成了她的创作素材。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708311818131dEbgWLrmwkQ7KYN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181814BEo2JST4LIzHPXhw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181813S1BvuWh35Ztx4Iwj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.294667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170831181813fVdCk9YGa1sg7beI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}